1. Decide pizza place
    1a. Pepperoni or cheese
    2b. Pepperoni
2. Decide what type of pizza to order
3. Call the pizza place
4. Order the pizza
    4a. Pay over phone
    4b. Pay at door
5. Wait for delivery driver
6. Greet delivery driver
7. See step 4b if necessary 
8.Order more pizza if still hungry